    "description": "《米诺陶：迷宫》是一个多人（最多5对1）恐怖游戏，在其中一名玩家成为强大的米诺陶，在一个随即生成的迷宫中追击试图逃离的人类囚犯。<br><br>人类可以装备特殊技能并寻找各种装备来帮助他们逃离迷宫。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/da7c9e24649e80196be69d0657239812.poster.avif?t=1731672204\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/da7c9e24649e80196be69d0657239812.webm?t=1731672204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/da7c9e24649e80196be69d0657239812.mp4?t=1731672204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/e5cd233be4b2db28e58a75a047406ec8.avif?t=1731672204\" width=601 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/6e47dc0d6e8efbf9c16d11b8e1f38094.poster.avif?t=1731672204\" width=300 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/6e47dc0d6e8efbf9c16d11b8e1f38094.webm?t=1731672204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/6e47dc0d6e8efbf9c16d11b8e1f38094.mp4?t=1731672204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你有机会扮演强大的米诺陶，一只可怕的生物，拥有无与伦比的力量和智慧。利用你卓越的感知和能力逐一追捕试图逃离迷宫的人类。<br><br>撞破墙壁，并利用你的能力将猎物逼入死角。你是终极捕食者，拥抱米诺陶的力量，让狩猎开始！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/109fb114cfa3329c3a5b8b2dd6effc99.avif?t=1731672204\" width=601 height=100 /></span><br>作为人类囚犯，你唯一的目标是在迷宫永久关闭之前逃离迷宫。运用智慧、装备、敏捷和环境来躲避米诺陶的愤怒。与其他人类一起使用语音聊天组队，或者为了生存而自私行动。你能否聪明地躲过米诺陶并逃离迷宫？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/8ccfc1c91291c4d14660f44398d8ac58.avif?t=1731672204\" width=601 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/7b64590f8929ef56c9757da554861c3f.poster.avif?t=1731672204\" width=300 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/7b64590f8929ef56c9757da554861c3f.webm?t=1731672204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/7b64590f8929ef56c9757da554861c3f.mp4?t=1731672204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>迷宫是随机生成的，意味着每场游戏都是独特且不可预测的经历，让你每次都紧张不安<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/7102c2eb97c9e8f5c6309735bf42d362.avif?t=1731672204\" width=601 height=100 /></span><br>作为房主，你有能力更改会话的许多方面，如迷宫大小、房间数量、出口数量、游戏时长、战利品数量、双方目标难度等等...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/0a177d83bdfefba0d7f26e0125a23e35.avif?t=1731672204\" width=601 height=100 /></span><br>独自与米诺陶人的AI对战，或与朋友一起游玩！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330210/extras/5f6170e0bc25d3e61182235cd7e66cf5.avif?t=1731672204\" width=601 height=100 /></span><br>解锁特殊技能、改进和角色定制选项。",
